  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Sea View Rooms</strong> are approx. 30-35 m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a rollaway bed) with wonderful sea views from the balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms</strong> are approx. 30-35 m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a rollaway bed). This room type is only available on a request basis, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Twin Superior Sea View Rooms</strong> are approx. 35-40 m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a rollaway bed). This room type is only available on a request basis, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are approx. 56 m² and sleep up to three people in twin beds (extra bed is a sofabed). Alternatively, this room can sleep two adults and two children. Junior suites offer a comfortable space with a small lounge area. This room type is only available on a request basis, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Single Standard Rooms</strong> are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Air-Conditioning </li>
<li>Mini-Bar (payable locally)</li>
<li>Smart TV </li>
<li>Room service </li>
<li>Tea making facilities </li>
<li>Bathrobe and slippers</li>
<li>Hairdryer </li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Change of towels 3 times per week or on request </li>
<li>Bed linen change 3 times per week or on request </li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>General information </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check in: 2pm</li>
<li>Check out: 12pm </li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of approx. €2.00 per person per night, for a maximum of 7 nights is payable locally for guests age 13 years and over (subject to change).</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>
<p>Accessible rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
